{"tid":771701,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"大蛇屙尿！ 袁文傑真係見過！","createTime":"2018-08-08T07:29:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-08T13:02:13.000Z","uid":160973,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f8709e26ef3c0c96d8433b3dffc57dbd0eb960e5","tid":771701,"uid":160973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T07:29:25.000Z","msg":"經常有人霸氣問，「有無見過大蛇屙尿先？」<br />\n聽落好似好型，但實際都幾污穢！袁文傑日前於社交平台擺放當年在亞視做節目主持時的片段，節目中他頸纏大蛇，唔知係咪托得牠太舒服，突然殺他一個個措手不及，來一招真正的大蛇屙尿！令他當場愕然！但礙於節目繼續播，佢都要保持鎮定做埋落去，坐在旁的師傅就話：「呢啲鏡頭唔播啦！」<br />\n問返袁文傑，究竟做咩節目有咁好嘅奇遇？佢話：「我都唔記得咩節目，但因為唔想將條蛇就咁擺响到，所以就纏上頸，而且牠都好乖，但點知突然屙尿，我都嚇左一跳！」所以大家下次見到袁文傑就唔好問佢，有無見過大蛇屙尿喇！佢真係見過㗎！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Omldlq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Omldlq&d=OSYCL8qBPEKgVfYrwvjrwgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=c35f6881\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Omldlq</a>"},{"pid":"f49b4d81d2d1b98ab2e36b37cd03ac7d5db3c647","tid":771701,"uid":132587,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T07:30:16.000Z","msg":"咁都可以做新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86353ea66a1f67921b7da77cb8e43df3e6e607d2","tid":771701,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T07:40:42.000Z","msg":"馬英九看手錶"},{"pid":"14decad3a35915be03f0398b4db151d877590b9a","tid":771701,"uid":53254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T08:20:30.000Z","msg":"發現洋娃娃"},{"pid":"ef1de13121c8b54932adc5b68e352309ff85764a","tid":771701,"uid":44454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T08:25:33.000Z","msg":"斬豬肉嚇親馬英九"},{"pid":"bebb4b38336b8e252c241628d62b5e59a151f6e0","tid":771701,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T13:02:13.000Z","msg":"屎定尿"}]}